    "asOf": "2019-05-07",
    "date": "2020-02-20T20:47:50Z",
    "text": "Honest Ads Act\n\nThis bill applies requirements, limitations, and protections regarding political advertising in traditional media to internet or digital political advertising. The bill sets forth special rules for disclosure statements for certain internet or digital ads.\n\nEach television or radio station, provider of cable or satellite television, or online platform must ensure that the political advertising it hosts is not directly or indirectly purchased by a foreign national.\n\nOnline platforms must publish a record of requests to purchase political advertising."
